OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy morning with outbreaks
OL,6,Fof light rain or drizzle. Mainly dry
OL,7,Fin the afternoon but a few showers
OL,8,Fwill develop over the Angus and
OL,9,FPerthshire hills.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will be a cloudy evening
OL,12,Fwith a few light showers around.
OL,13,FShowers dying out overnight with some
OL,14,Fclear spells developing.
OL,15,
OL,16,CMonday:FDry through the morning and
OL,17,Ffor much of the afternoon with good
OL,18,Fsunny spells. Turning cloudy with some
OL,19,Fshowers spreading east through late
OL,20,Fafternoon and evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
